This file is a placeholder because the canonical license text
could not be fetched from the environment where the repo was
prepared. Before publishing, replace this file with the full AGPL-3.0
text using one of the commands below.

Option 1 — fetch from the FSF (canonical source):

    curl -o LICENSE https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.txt

Option 2 — copy the exact LICENCE.md that RustDesk ships:

    curl -L -o LICENSE https://raw.githubusercontent.com/rustdesk/rustdesk/master/LICENCE.md

Once this file contains the real AGPL-3.0 text, GitHub will
automatically detect it and show "AGPL-3.0" on your repo homepage.
